{"tid":1102551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有日本女朋友就係咁撚正","createTime":"2019-04-11T19:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T15:11:48.000Z","uid":150079,"like":35,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"304eb59f040ea062e50ad6976f343346c4baa78c","tid":1102551,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7mABIqZAANk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7mABIqZAANk&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=61aac901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7mABIqZAANk</a><br />\n我女朋友仲多個呢一個優點，佢唔會用我銀包啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同埋日本妹會係你面前落妝，都係咁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完呢條片係咪覺得溝日本妹算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算，港女死開啦飯都唔識煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係鍾意做港女兵啊吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72130c6559cbfa9fe530dc6afd40a5fee57172b","tid":1102551,"uid":137743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T19:40:42.000Z","msg":"首先"},{"pid":"2af40501bdcd81186de5e1d8c777f525d0cab88a","tid":1102551,"uid":150079,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T19:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHMq197.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHMq197.png&h=27a53c98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FzW8Qa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FzW8Qa.png&h=e247e447&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbBnjWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbBnjWS.png&h=ab71627f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZLSHae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZLSHae.png&h=9abca741&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTSNv3B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTSNv3B.png&h=23ba351d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港粥都識煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又識整東坡肉，台灣滷肉飯又識整，所以唔存在日本妹淨係識整日本菜"},{"pid":"009d88d63752b614a1e549f989e6f35f0f429500","tid":1102551,"uid":195975,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T19:43:45.000Z","msg":"我都好想有女朋友啊...<br />\n<br />\n不過我呢種絕對無用既廢物點會有女仔睇中?<br />\n<br />\n猥褻 卑鄙 悲觀 消極 膽小 內向 老土 醜樣 愚蠢 自私 淫賤 咸濕 懶惰 性無能<br />\n<br />\n簡直係浪費地球資源,自殺又無膽,究竟幾時先死...<br />\n<br />\n我都好懷疑自己仲有冇資格生存<br />\n<br />\n我人生無目標，搵過社工佢都覺得我無咩用<br />\n<br />\n因為長期無同人接觸，精神科醫生話我有焦慮症<br />\n<br />\n我除左每日返工放工返工放工，<br />\n<br />\n咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n想出街又出唔到，又唔知去邊<br />\n<br />\n朋友都無多個<br />\n<br />\n女朋友更加唔使講，網上搵過又唔得，現實又唔得<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得做人好煩厭十分之難<br />\n<br />\n睇左毒神阿源既故事<br />\n<br />\n我都好想改變自己，做返個有用既人，開開心心<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位幫下我，我真係唔知可以點做，比次機會我改變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/